JSON SERVER
CREATE A JSON PACKAGE
1. create folder A for server
mkdir NAME
2. go into folder, run the following
npm init
npm install json-server
run npm install json-server ngrok .(optional) 

--INSIDE OF FOLDER A
1. to initiate the server 
npm run db
2. to initiate ngrok
npm run tunnel

